<taxonomicName id="4C72B0A15215FFABFE947EE92AB6F2E5" authority="Fitzgerald, 2020" authorityName="Fitzgerald" authorityYear="2020" box="[347,430,1224,1247]" class="Insecta" family="Ditomyiidae" genus="Ditomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="255" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nana" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="B90617305215FFABFE947EE92AB6F2E5" box="[347,430,1224,1247]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="255">D. nana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A235AA4B5215FFABFE7B7EE92AF5F2E5" box="[436,493,1224,1247]" pageId="16" pageNumber="255" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, head. 40. Male, holotype, anterior view. 41. Female, paratype, lateral view. Scale bars = ca. 0.25 mm. Abbreviations: fs, frontal suture; lo, lateral ocellus; mo, median ocellus; mp1, maxillary palpus one; mp2, maxillary palpus two; v, vertex.
</paragraph>
